==English==
===Etymology===
Probably from reference to a [[board game]].

===Phrase===
'''back to square one'''
#{{idiom}} Back to the [[start]], as after a [[dead-end]] or [[failure]].
#: ''After spending six hours on the intake we realized that there was nothing wrong with it, so I guess it's '''back to square one'''.''

===Translations===
* {{sv}} : [[tillbaka till ruta ett]]

